snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Maria | Osho x Mansa x Arijit x Shillong Chamber Choir x Bombay Brass
snippet.description:
A nostalgic melody from the evergreen loved song ‘O Maria’ finally sees the story completed between Johnny, Maria & Maria’s Father.
The song features Osho Jain, who has won hearts with his unique songs, and Mansa Pandey, known for her unique covers of timeless classics. They are accompanied by Shillong Chamber Choir, celebrated for their harmonious performances, talented composer-singer Arijit Datta, a popular name in the indie-rock scene with renowned saxophonist Rhys Sebastian’s Bombay Brass, India’s first modern baraat & independent brass band.

Composer: Rhys Sebastian, Arijit Datta
